Stage4:
cd codebook
virtualenv venv
source venv/bin/activate && cd codex
pip install -r requirements.txt
#create .env file and add configuration
vim .env
Run Server:

/home/ubuntu/codebook/venv/bin/gunicorn codex.wsgi:application --bind 0.0.0.0:8000 --workers 2

